==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Foot ton
<hw>Foot ton</hw>. <fld>(Mech.)</fld> <def>A unit of energy or work,
being equal to the work done in raising one ton against the force of
gravity through the height of one foot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Foot valve</ent>⟦br⟧
